{"tid":1879176,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「臨床診斷」計入確診數致病例狂升","createTime":"2020-02-14T04:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T04:59:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3678e2343ecfdaf511d889f86f9b48e97bb84c4","tid":1879176,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200214/HN7DICCZ3C5STKJYGZXUCY5M5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200214%2FHN7DICCZ3C5STKJYGZXUCY5M5Q%2F&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKRw4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=a8a08093\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200214%2FHN7DICCZ3C5STKJYGZXUCY5M5Q%2F&h=55b22649\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200214/HN7DICCZ3C5STKJYGZXUCY5M5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n「臨床診斷」計入確診數致病例狂升<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200214/large/1581611914_4283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200214%2Flarge%2F1581611914_4283.jpg&h=353b6705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身穿保護衣的武漢醫護人員，累倒值班室。路透社<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】內地日前修訂《新冠狀病毒病人感染的肺炎診療方案》，當中湖北省放寬疑似病例標準，並由只有疑似及確診個案，再加上臨床診斷病例。<span style=\"color: orange;\">若疑似個案病人經X光或電腦掃描有肺炎迹象，即使未經核酸測試，也列為臨床診斷病例。</span><br />\n<br />\n湖北衞健委昨起，將對以往疑似病例展開調查，而昨新公佈的確診數字，已包含了「臨床診斷」的確診數，故湖北確診病例一下子暴增近1.5萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅湖北放寬標準<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：良田村病人 妻母無隔離<br />\n<br />\n不過，上海衞健委表示，除湖北外，其他省市還是將核酸檢測作為唯一確診標準。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">湖北醫院此前斷診的唯一手段是核酸檢測，惟核酸檢測試劑盒一直供不應求，準確率更只有30%至50%，導致病人即使流行病學史、臨床症狀脗合，甚至電腦掃描顯示，肺部病毒感染，一旦核酸檢測呈陰性，也不能稱為確診。</span><br />\n<br />\n湖北衞健委/財新網"},{"pid":"09a4dc0977e43305efa0e93cccb8028aba1ae4a4","tid":1879176,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"本來已經報細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}